## Implementation Plan: Extracting Business Logic into a Service Layer

### Overview

The refactor introduces three new files under `src/services/` and rewrites the two route files to be thin HTTP adapters. No other files change. The boundary rule is strict: routes own parsing, shape validation, and response; services own all domain logic and throw `AppError` on domain failures.

